x step-1 was applied), so `horizon commit` should work once the work is finished and verified.\n\n**Recommended human action:** kill the stale PID `47819` if confirmed hung, then relaunch a clean T2/picrep session to finish and verify the pile (full `lake build`) before committing. See `recommendation.md`.",
